    {
        "url": "/quotes/xavier_dolan_736782",
        "quote": "My extreme characters are in a state of rebellion or who are being ostracized or being misunderstood, or misfits or trying to fit in and fighting for their rights to love, live, and co-exist. They sort of mirror my own demons.",
